RedmineLesiteBulkAdjustVersionDeadlines
=======================================

This plugin adds an iteration length field to project settings form,
and an “adjust all subsequent versions” checkbox to versions form.

When adjust all subsequent version is checked, the dates of all versions due after the current version will be adjusted.
Versions with null dates will be assigned dates.


Installation Notes
==================
* Add a custom field in Projects:
    Name: Iteration Length In Days
    Type: Integer
    Required: True
    Default: 7

* Add a custom field in Versions:
		Name: Adjust All Subsequent Versions
		Type: Boolean
		For all projects: True
		Tracker: Deliverable


